    "constitutionalAuthorityStatementText": "<pre>\n[Congressional Record Volume 171, Number 13 (Wednesday, January 22, 2025)]\n[House]\nFrom the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href=\"https://www.gpo.gov\">www.gpo.gov</a>]\nBy Mr. McCAUL:\nH.R. 625.\nCongress has the power to enact this legislation pursuant\nto the following:\nArticle 1 Section 8\nAmends Title 28, United States Code, to authorize holding\ncourt in College Station, Texas and El Centro, California.\n[Page H300]\n</pre>",
